reviewText: if you see desert island classics on top of the movie don't buy it!!! ive bought maybe to other desert island classics before  and it literally copied right off of VHS normally that wouldnt be a bad thing however desert island classics completely just chop up the movie everything is outta sync and its just not watchable at all.
Half the DVD is out of sync and the nudity is all blurred out. The quality looks like a bootleg tape.
